column1:
Precision of the real price rounding. Not to be confused with display precision that can be configured in extension ET Currency Manager.
Examples:
2 => 14.46
1 => 14.50
0 => 15.00

Примеры:
2 => 14.46
1 => 14.50
0 => 15.00
